features: This listing is for CHILD SIZES only. FOR ADULT SIZES OF THIS SAME ITEM, click on "SILVERFISH" above to see our full catalog of items.

Customize Your Own Basketball tank top jersey exactly how you want it! Create your own! Choose your size and color, and then click ""Customize Now"" to enter your personalization. Perfect For teams, leagues, or the casual fan! Fun novelty! Makes a great gift! ***THERE ARE NO RETURNS ON CUSTOMIZED PRODUCTS!***

Adult and Youth sizes are available - See our full catalog for more sizing options. (YXS, YS, YM, YL, YXL, S, M, L, XL, 2XL, 3XL, 4XL). Sizing chart included in images to find your perfect fit. Unisex Fit. Men/Women Boys/Girls.
3.6-ounce, 100% polyester mesh with PosiCharge technology. White mesh reverse.
